snippet.title: Hitman  Sniper Assassins | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: From the makers of the acclaimed Hitman Sniper, we are proud to announce Project Hitman Sniper Assassins (working title) a wholly original Hitman story, with new playable assassins and brand-new gameplay features, developed by Square Enix Montréal. Coming 2021 on iOS and Android, and we’ll have more to share in the future.
